                     <interp inst="t18120916-131-off726" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18120916-131-off726" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18120916-131-cd727" type="crimeDate">1st of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120916-131-off726 t18120916-131-cd727"></join>, two waistcoats, value 5 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18120916-131-victim1115" type="victimName">
                        Moses 
                        Barnard
                     <interp inst="t18120916-131-victim1115" type="surname" value="Barnard"></interp>
